We are using self-hosted runners on OVH Cloud (Singapore region).

- Infrastructure: OVH Cloud, Ubuntu 22.04, 2 vCPUs, 7GB RAM (b2-7)
- Repository: dojima-foundation/tee-auth (repository-level runners)
- Labels: ["ovh", "self-hosted", "ubuntu-22.04"]
- Features: Docker support, health monitoring, status pages
- Access: SSH with key authentication, health checks every 5 minutes
- Management: Terraform-based infrastructure, automated setup

